title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast, June 5: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks had relatively quiet holiday-shortened week, at least where major indexes were concerned. The Dow Industrials (DJI), S&P 500 (SP500), and Nasdaq Composite (COMP.IND) rallied today to finish in the green: The Dow and S&P gained about 0.6% week-over-week, with the Nasdaq adding about 0.5%.  Learn more about your ad choices.
